      "content": "i feel like there's nothing left of me. i used to look at a canvas and see a world, but now i just look at my hands and they feel like... tools for a person who doesn't exist anymore. the spark is just gone. it's like the light went out and left a hollow shell behind. i'm just walking around in an empty room.",
